00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:35.000
We'll build a REST API endpoint with validation and error handling.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:43.000
Then we'll write comprehensive unit tests using Copilot's test generation features.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:51.000
Finally, we'll refactor legacy code with Copilot's assistance.

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:59.000
Watch how natural language descriptions guide the code generation process.

